About Us

We are a united CTF team from Malaysia.
Our team was made up primarily of members from SKR, Verdesec, and Hibiscus Lab.

Our Goals

Our goal is to support the growth of Malaysia's CTF and cybersecurity communities by inspiring more newcomers to join the field.

CTF Participation

We regularly participate in Capture The Flag (CTF) competitions to enhance our skills and knowledge in cybersecurity.

Knowledge Sharing

We conduct sessions to exchange our knowledge and experiences with each other.

Team Gatherings

Occasionally, we meet in person to enjoy participating in CTFs together.
